{"tid":1809381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3名中國女子放天燈引致德國大火","createTime":"2020-01-03T05:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T07:36:49.000Z","uid":122558,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f58106b7f8a6ef91f6994d9f3e74caed1f9fe064","tid":1809381,"uid":122558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:09:30.000Z","msg":"德國北萊因-西發利亞邦(North Rhine-Westphalia)克里菲德市(Krefeld)當局今天(2日)表示，1名中國婦女和她2名已成年的女兒，因為歡度新年除夕放天燈慶祝，造成當地動物園大火，數十隻動物死亡，其中包括8隻猩猩。<br />\n<br />\n克里菲德鄰近荷蘭邊界。<br />\n<br />\n克里菲德警方表示，這3名女性在獲悉這起災難之後，已經向警方自首，而在火災中死亡的動物包括：5隻猩猩、2隻大猩猩，以及1隻黑猩猩，另外還有許多狐蝠和鳥類。<br />\n<br />\n負責調查的霍普曼(Gerd Hoppmann)今天在記者會上表示，德國大多數地方禁止燃放天燈已經10年，但這3名女性卻認為可以在除夕夜燃放，並透過網路購買了5盞天燈。<br />\n<br />\n霍普曼表示：「我曾看過許多人類的屍體，而我在看到這些大猩猩的屍體被燒得變形時，非常震撼，因為跟人類太像了。」<br />\n<br />\n這3名女子在天燈上寫了祝福新年的字句，其中4個落在動物園附近，第五個則引起動物園大火。<br />\n<br />\n這3名婦女可能因為疏忽引發大火面臨起訴，一旦定罪最高可能被判處5年監禁或罰款。<br />\n<br />\n不過，霍普曼也表示，這3名女子很勇敢的出面投案，值得尊敬。<br />\n<br />\n動物園今天停止開放，許多淚流滿面的遊客在動物園門口點燃蠟燭，並獻花致意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/tw.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2587%2588%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB-3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25A6%2596-133800074.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2F%2525E5%2525A4%2525A9%2525E7%252587%252588%2525E8%252587%2525B4%2525E5%2525BE%2525B7%2525E5%25259C%25258B%2525E5%25258B%252595%2525E7%252589%2525A9%2525E5%25259C%252592%2525E5%2525A4%2525A7%2525E7%252581%2525AB-3%2525E4%2525B8%2525AD%2525E5%25259C%25258B%2525E5%2525A5%2525B3%2525E5%2525AD%252590%2525E8%252587%2525AA%2525E9%2525A6%252596-133800074.html&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7CIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=06f99212\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/tw.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2587%2588%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB-3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25A6%2596-133800074.html</a>"},{"pid":"a5bc56749e67c6f93165759979a43b929c5617eb","tid":1809381,"uid":123926,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"中國人去到邊衰到邊系列"},{"pid":"42dc397d879221bdb46149a44800e9e95a9bf309","tid":1809381,"uid":65289,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"寧願坐監都要留o係德國唔返支那"},{"pid":"f5adc6e9800f5ffd97bf20146872cd343decbdf4","tid":1809381,"uid":38518,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:13:13.000Z","msg":"死刑啦"},{"pid":"9e3caf68441fe87629eade6d92e2c3c09ff4327c","tid":1809381,"uid":122558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"42dc397d879221bdb46149a44800e9e95a9bf309","tid":1809381,"uid":65289,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"寧願坐監都要留o係德國唔返支那"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1126dece2def9809405b7f875decf6935285fcf6","tid":1809381,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5bc56749e67c6f93165759979a43b929c5617eb","tid":1809381,"uid":123926,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"中國人去到邊衰到邊系列"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:36:30.000Z","msg":"全部禁入境應該"},{"pid":"8136daaf33b518cce3f9d3ca37f1fec2ec3629b5","tid":1809381,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"就算支那人識知衰, 但都係冇常識, 唔知幾時會整啲乜嘢大鑊嘢, 唔應該俾佢哋入境"},{"pid":"57b5d58da33160572eea2183951c0c4c1ab4cbb5","tid":1809381,"uid":159881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"不過，霍普曼也表示，這3名女子很勇敢的出面投案，值得尊敬。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo